SIMPLE: diversely
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Diversely
<hw>Di"verse*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>In
different ways; differently; variously.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Diversely</xex> interpreted.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>How <qex>diversely</qex> love doth his pageants play.</q>
<rj><qau>Spenser.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>In different directions; to different
points.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>On life's vast ocean <qex>diversely</qex> we sail.</q>
<rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Diverseness</ent>⟦br⟧
